descPeakActivePowerConsumed: peak effective power consumed within 15 minutes interval
descPeakActivePowerProduced: peak effective power produced within 15 minutes interval
descActiveEnergyT1Consumed: total effective energy consumed during HT time
descActiveEnergyT2Consumed: total effective energy consumed during LT time
descActiveEnergyT1Produced: total effective energy produced during HT time
descActiveEnergyT2Produced: total effective energy produced during HT time
descPower: totalized effective power (positive value indicates consumed power)
descInfoOnline: device is online and transmits data
descHistory: data averaged over specified time interval
descCurrStart: value at start of current interval
descLastStart: value at start of last interval
descMinute: data summarized over an interval of 1 minute
descQuarter: data summarized over an interval of 15 minutes
descHour: data summarized over an interval of 1 hour
descDay: data summarized over an interval of 1 day
descInfoRate: number of updates received from device per minute
